# Turbo monorepo

## Workspace

- Root `package.json` orchestrates via **Turbo**
- Workspaces: `apps/*`, `packages/*` (`pnpm-workspace.yaml`)
- Internal deps: `"@repo/ui": "workspace:*"`

## Scripts (run from root)

| Script | Effect |
|--------|--------|
| `pnpm dev:web` | `turbo dev --filter=web` |
| `pnpm build` | All packages build (dependsOn `^build`) |
| `pnpm lint` / `pnpm typecheck` | Per-package via Turbo |

## Adding packages

- App → `apps/<name>/package.json` + register in workspace
- Shared lib → `packages/<name>/`
- Add Turbo tasks in `turbo.json` if new task types appear

## Don't

- Use npm or yarn
- Put app-specific UI in `apps/web/components` - use `@repo/ui`
- Edit `pnpm-lock.yaml` by hand
